    <title>What are acids and bases</title>
    <p>
		<term>Summary:</term>
	</p>

	<p><ol>
				
		<li>
            <p>
                Acids donate <m>H^+</m> ions to other things and increase the amount of <m>H^+</m> in a solution
            </p>
        </li>
 
        <li>
            <p>
                Bases accept <m>H^+</m> ions and increase the amount of <m>OH^-</m> in a solution
            </p>
        </li>

    </ol></p>
